OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA woman stabbed her ex-partner to
OL,8,Fdeath after "planning" the attack with
OL,9,Fher daughter and her partner, a court
OL,10,Fhas heard.
OL,12,FHelen Shakespeare, her daughter
OL,13,FLetisha Goodwin, 30, and Anthony
OL,14,FHillier, 33, are charged with the
OL,15,Fmurder of Raymond Groves, 48, from
OL,16,FBristol, on 2 July last year.
OL,18,FKate Lumsdon KC, prosecuting, told
OL,19,FSalisbury Crown Court that Goodwin had
OL,20,Fcalled police at about 8pm that night.
