OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe said she had returned from the
OL,8,Fshops to the home she shared with her
OL,9,Fmother in Strawberry Fields,
OL,10,FEasterton, Wiltshire, and found "a man
OL,11,Flying on the floor with blood
OL,12,Feverywhere".
OL,14,FPolice, paramedics and a doctor
OL,15,Fattended the home, where they found
OL,16,Fthe victim, who had been "repeatedly
OL,17,Fstabbed", lying face down on the hall
OL,18,Ffloor with a knife in his left hand,
OL,19,Fanother on the floor and one in the
OL,20,Fkitchen sink.
