OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Lumsdon said that Shakespeare, 53,
OL,8,Ftold them that Mr Groves, with whom
OL,9,Fshe had previously been in a
OL,10,Frelationship for "many years", had
OL,11,Fattempted to rape her.
OL,13,FThe prosecutor said: "It looked at
OL,14,Ffirst blush like the desperate attempt
OL,15,Fof a woman to protect herself from an
OL,16,Fintruder.
OL,18,F"It looked like Miss Goodwin had
OL,19,Fstumbled on a situation of which she
OL,20,Fhad no knowledge.
OL,26,@rD@ROUrD@]O]uD@VOUzD@AOU
