OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,F"As the investigation unfolded, it
OL,8,Fbecame clear that there was more to
OL,9,Fthis situation than meets the eye.
OL,11,F"By piecing together evidence from a
OL,12,Fnumber of sources, including material
OL,13,Ffrom telephones, the Crown suggests
OL,14,Fthat the true situation is that far
OL,15,Ffrom being a spontaneous act of
OL,16,Fpassion, it was a killing that had
OL,17,Fbeen planned."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUyD@NO]
