OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe prosecutor said that messages sent
OL,8,Fbetween Goodwin and Hillier appeared
OL,9,Fto show them discussing stabbing Mr
OL,10,FGroves.
OL,12,FOn June 18, Hillier, of Royal Wootton
OL,13,FBassett, wrote to Goodwin: "You're
OL,14,Fplaying with fire baby if you stab
OL,15,Fhim. Your mum can stab him, I'm not
OL,16,Fgetting you in trouble."
OL,26,@uD@\OUxD@XO]
