OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMs Lumsdon said that Hillier also
OL,8,Fwrote that he would do it, to which
OL,9,FGoodwin replied: "I don't want anyone
OL,10,Fto do my dirty work for me, I'm a
OL,11,Fgrown-arse woman."
OL,13,FMs Lumsdon said that a post-mortem
OL,14,Fexamination showed that Mr Groves
OL,15,Fsuffered 12 stab wounds, including
OL,16,Fthree to his neck that severed his
OL,17,Fjugular vein, and four wounds to his
OL,18,Fback which cut up to 12.5cm deep.
OL,26,@qD@ROUsD@RO]
