OL,3,CWoman 'planned' murder of ex-partner
OL,4,Cwith daughter and her partner, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe had also suffered 11 "defence"
OL,8,Fwounds to his right hand, and two on
OL,9,Fhis left hand, which Ms Lumsdon said
OL,10,Fwas consistent with him attempting to
OL,11,F"grab a knife or ward off a knife" to
OL,12,Fprotect himself.
OL,14,FMs Lumsdon said that Mr Groves had
OL,15,Fvisited Shakespeare on 27 June, when
OL,16,Fthe prosecution claim there was an
OL,17,Faborted attempt by her to stab him,
OL,18,Fthe events of 2 July being a second
OL,19,Fattempt.
