OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FShe said that Shakespeare told police
OL,8,Fthat Mr Groves had "forced his way"
OL,9,Finto the house "with a glint in his
OL,10,Fface" before "forcing himself" upon
OL,11,Fher, and she had "grabbed a kitchen
OL,12,Fknife" in self-defence.
OL,14,FThe defendants deny the charge and the
OL,15,Ftrial continues.
